NEW marauder.1.desc:1 "Having decoded what counts as a language among them, [This.Owner.GetEnvoy] [This.Leader.GetName] has identified the §H[encountered_marauder.GetName]§! as a nomadic civilization known as the §H[encountered_marauder.GetRealName]§!. They occupy a number of large space stations in and around the §H[marauder_system.GetName]§! system that house the bulk of their massive numbers in crowded and squalid conditions. Despite this, or perhaps because of it, they seem to have developed a strong martial culture. Life in the cold void has become second nature to them, and they are very adept at space warfare.\n\nThere is no [encountered_marauder.GetSpeciesName] central government to speak of. Instead, they are divided into several different factions that vie endlessly with one another for resources and respect. Given their large population and the shipbuilding capability of their stations, this constant infighting is the only thing keeping them from growing into a significant threat to galactic peace."
OLD marauder.1.desc:0 "We have made first contact with the §H[encountered_marauder.GetName]§!, a nomadic civilization. They occupy a number of large space stations in and around the §H[marauder_system.GetName]§! system that house the bulk of their massive numbers in crowded and squalid conditions. Despite this, or perhaps because of it, they seem to have developed a strong martial culture. Life in the cold void has become second nature to them, and they are very adept at space warfare.\n\nThere is no [encountered_marauder.GetSpeciesName] central government to speak of. Instead, they are divided into several different factions that vie endlessly with one another for resources and respect. Given their large population and the shipbuilding capability of their stations, this constant infighting is the only thing keeping them from growing into a significant threat to galactic peace."
CN  marauder.1.desc:1 "我们第一次遇见了§H[encountered_marauder.GetName]§!，一个游牧文明。他们在§H[marauder_system.GetName]§!星系和周边地带占据了数个大型空间站，其大量的成员都居住在拥挤而肮脏的环境之中。尽管如此，也许正因如此，他们似乎发展出了一种非常尚武的文化。冰冷虚空中的生活成了他们的第二天性，而且他们非常擅长太空战事。\n\n[encountered_marauder.GetSpeciesName]无代表全国的中央政府，而是分为数个不同的派系，不断地互相争夺资源和权势。鉴于其庞大的人口和空间站的造船能力，这无休止的内斗是唯一能阻止他们严重威胁银河系和平的事情。"
CN2 marauder.1.desc:1 "我们完成了对他们使用语言的破译，[This.Owner.GetEnvoy][This.Leader.GetName]将§H[encountered_marauder.GetName]§!识别为一种游牧文明，称为§H[encountered_marauder.GetRealName]§!。他们在§H[marauder_system.GetName]§!恒星系附近占据了数个大型空间站，其大量的人口都居住在拥挤而肮脏的环境之中。尽管如此，或许正因如此，他们似乎发展出了一种非常尚武的文化。生活在冰冷虚空中成了他们的第二天性，因而高度擅长太空作战。\n\n[encountered_marauder.GetSpeciesName]没有中央政府一说，而是分为数个不同的派系，不断地互相争夺资源与尊严。鉴于其庞大的人口与空间站造船能力，若无永无止境的内斗，他们必将成为严重威胁到全星系和平的势力。"
NEW marauder.508.desc:2 "This is Great Khan [great_khan.GetName] of the [From.GetName]. My defeat at the hands of the [khan_destroyer.GetRealName] was a minor setback - nothing more. The [khan_destroyer.GetSpeciesNamePlural] are brave warriors and worthy opponents, but they, too, will fall before us.\n\nThe tide of history is sweeping across the galaxy, and nothing can stop it. My new armada has been assembled."
OLD marauder.508.desc:1 "This is Great Khan [great_khan.GetName] of the [From.GetName]. My defeat at the hands of the [khan_destroyer.GetName] was a minor setback - nothing more. The [khan_destroyer.GetSpeciesNamePlural] are brave warriors and worthy opponents, but they, too, will fall before us.\n\nThe tide of history is sweeping across the galaxy, and nothing can stop it. My new armada has been assembled."
CN  marauder.508.desc:2 "我是[From.GetName]的大可汗[great_khan.GetName]。我在[khan_destroyer.GetName]手中遭受的失败仅仅是个小小的挫折，这什么也说明不了。[khan_destroyer.GetSpeciesNamePlural]是勇敢的战士，也是值得交手的对手。但是，他们终将在我们之前毁灭。\n\n历史的浪潮正在席卷整个银河系，什么也无法阻挡战车的车轮。我们新的大舰队已经组建完毕。"
CN2 marauder.508.desc:2 "吾乃[From.GetName]之天可汗，[great_khan.GetName]。吾在[khan_destroyer.GetName]的溃败不过只是寸兵尺铁的损失罢了。[khan_destroyer.GetSpeciesNamePlural]是一群勇敢的战士，是可敬的对手，但他们仍逃不了被吾击败的命运。\n\n星河潮流浩浩荡荡，顺之者昌，逆之者亡。我的全新舰队已经筹备好了。"
ADD marauder.524.name:0 "Great Khan Presumed Dead"
CN2 marauder.524.name:0 "据信大可汗已死"
ADD marauder.524.a.desc:0 "Despite concerns that the Great Khan would somehow resurface at the head of a new battle fleet, the utter defeat of the Horde seems to have made that impossible.\n\nAlthough no body has been found, the Great Khan is believed to have died when the last of the Horde's stations and starships were destroyed."
CN2 marauder.524.a.desc:0 "尽管大可汗是否还会重出江湖、出现在某一支新舰队上的念头仍让人忧心忡忡，但从部落的全面失利看来这种可能性微乎其微。\n\n虽然其尸首下落不明，但据信大可汗还是在最后一个部落的空间站和战舰被摧毁的时候战死了。"
ADD marauder.524.b.desc:0 "$marauder.524.a.desc$\n\nMeanwhile, our crews have continued to sift through the wreckage of the Khan's former flagship. They found a large blood-stained chair floating in space, and are reasonably certain that this piece of furniture was, in fact, the Great Khan's throne."
CN2 marauder.524.b.desc:0 "$marauder.524.a.desc$\n\n与此同时，我们的船员仍继续在前可汗舰队的残骸中搜寻。他们发现了一座漂浮在太空中的巨大染血座椅，并且基本可以肯定这一张座椅就是大可汗的王座。"
ADD marauder.524.a:0 "Good riddance!"
CN2 marauder.524.a:0 "谢天谢地！"
ADD marauder.524.b:0 "An excellent find."
CN2 marauder.524.b:0 "了不起的发现。"
